name: Riders of Apocalypse - Famine
description:
When the Whale broke the third seal, I heard the third living creature saying,
"Come." I looked, and behold, a black fish; and he who sat on it had a pair of scales in his back.
And I heard something like a voice in the center of the four living creatures saying,
"A quart of wheat for a denarius, and three quarts of barley for a denarius;
but do not damage the oil and the wine."
